Class Ticket

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.travlendarplus.entities.GenericEntity
      • it.polimi.travlendarplus.entities.EntityWithLongKey
        • it.polimi.travlendarplus.entities.tickets.Ticket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DistanceTicket, GenericTicket, PeriodTicket

    @Entity(name="ABSTRACT_TICKET")
public abstract class Ticket
extends EntityWithLongKey
    This JPA abstract class represent a generic ticket, to be implemented by all ticket's classes
